Apr 25
In kiosk app in Debian i solve this by putting these lines to ~/.xinitrc

echo "" > ~/.config/google-chrome/Profile\ 1/Current\ Session
echo "" > ~/.config/google-chrome/Profile\ 1/Current\ Tabs
echo "" > ~/.config/google-chrome/Profile\ 1/Last\ Session
echo "" > ~/.config/google-chrome/Profile\ 1/Last\ Tabs
